<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠٩ ـ مِنْ مُسَنْدِ عَدِيِّ بْنِ عُمَيْرَةَ الْحَضْرَمِيِّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَحَدِ بَنِي أَرْقَمَ، وَهُوَ أَخُو الْعُرْسِيِّ بْنِ عَمِيرَةَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدِيثُهُ فِي رَابِعِ الشَّامِيِّينَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>